name: coinfident/influencer_explorer
description: Influencer Explorer is an agent for exploring crypto influencers on Twitter, delivering actionable insights and sentiment analysis. Tracking 3,700 influencers and 75 news outlets, it provides analytics and buy/not-buy signals for over 30 coins.
